thread.title: BRIEF-Spirit Of Texas Bancshares Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $46 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Spirit Of Texas Bancshares Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $46 Mln
text:
April 6, 2018 / 5:00 PM / Updated 9 minutes ago BRIEF-Spirit Of Texas Bancshares Inc Files For IPO Of Up To $46 Mln Reuters Staff 
April 6 (Reuters) - Spirit of Texas Bancshares Inc: 
* SPIRIT OF TEXAS BANCSHARES INC FILES FOR IPO OF UP TO $46 MILLION – SEC FILING 
* SPIRIT OF TEXAS BANCSHARES INC SAYS IT INTENDS TO APPLY TO HAVE ITS COMMON STOCK LISTED ON NASDAQ GLOBAL MARKET UNDER THE SYMBOL “STXB” 
* SPIRIT OF TEXAS BANCSHARES INC SAYS STEPHENS INC, KEEFE, BRUYETTE & WOODS, PIPER JAFFRAY ARE AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO 
* SPIRIT OF TEXAS BANCSHARES INC SAYS SANDLER O’NEILL + PARTNERS L.P. IS AMONG UNDERWRITERS TO IPO 
* SPIRIT OF TEXAS BANCSHARES INC SAYS PROPOSED IPO PRICE IS AN ESTIMATE SOLELY FOR CALCULATING SEC REGISTRATION FEE Source text: ( bit.ly/2HdF2ZE )
